# Turnover Log

## Stack
- API: ASP.NET Core 8, EF Core, SQL Server (LocalDB dev), Swashbuckle
- Client: React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind CSS v4
- Auth (upcoming): JWT — not implemented yet

## Conventions
- No secrets in git; use User Secrets and `.env` (client)
- New API endpoints need xUnit integration tests when behavior is non-trivial
- Keep commits small and descriptive
- API runs on http://localhost:5000; client on http://localhost:5173 with Vite `/api` proxy

## Structure
- `server/TurnoverLog.Api/` — Web API
- `client/` — React SPA
